; Coverage test for format.cc
; Test --force-color output path triggering ansify_if colorization.
; The register format with --force-color wraps account names and amounts
; in ANSI color codes, exercising the colorize path in parse_elements.

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --force-color
24-Jan-01 [1mGroceries            [0m [34mExpenses:Food         [0m       $10.00       $10.00
                                [34mAssets:Cash           [0m      [31m$-10.00[0m            0
end test
